<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870623-0016 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:Mayfair Super Markets Inc.</HL><DD> 06/23/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> MYFRADIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><TEXT>   MAYFAIR SUPER MARKETS INC., Elizabeth, N.J., declared a 2-for-1 split of the company's Class A and B common shares, but eliminated the two-cents-a-share dividend on the pre-split Class A stock. Mayfair said the split will be effective Aug. 24 to shareholders of record Aug. 10. The company said it doesn't pay a dividend on its Class B shares. Mayfair operates 33 Foodtown supermarkets in New Jersey. </TEXT></DOC>